{"tid":449032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有感而發] 其實2月29日出世嘅人都幾慘","createTime":"2017-10-26T19:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T05:38:11.000Z","uid":28938,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"73323cde4b809076c35a90b6dfe7cde3acb835b7","tid":449032,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T19:59:45.000Z","msg":"生日：<br />\n4年先有一次生日，雖然另外果三年都會慶祝，但感覺總無正日咁開心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日常社交：<br />\n俾人知道2月29日生日都會被串？「嘩，你4年先大一歲咁咪好正？」「嘩，你依家咪得7歲？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網：<br />\n成日上網做會員都搵唔到2月29日，次次都夾硬寫2月28日就算。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：4年生一次日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3602daa65b3eaf7910b0d3d175787ec2e6929eea","tid":449032,"uid":72638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T20:01:13.000Z","msg":"有個中學同學係咁<br />\n不過我地笑左幾次就算<br />\n大家都冇介意"},{"pid":"ffdc5973f9ddac38ba1495b741b8f3c5da8f826e","tid":449032,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T20:05:27.000Z","msg":"四年先大一歲<br />\n對女人來講咪正囉"},{"pid":"d2e70e8ebd0ce6e7005ddd49f483b5ed85b45efd","tid":449032,"uid":72638,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T20:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>四年先大一歲<br />\n對女人來講咪正囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但要72歲先可以合法扑野"},{"pid":"91b91e60a6c4a8787a4707ee5660f38102af810c","tid":449032,"uid":148599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T20:10:50.000Z","msg":"中學班入面有兩個係呢日生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f807d04f546be8e2a78c950641b5de947269619e","tid":449032,"uid":17313,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T20:11:51.000Z","msg":"好彩男朋友係2月28日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657cf79aa9fef2a993c9719f471fa85